      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a reliable workhorse with a bit of character? This vehicle is ready for someone who isn't afraid of a little DIY love! While it has significant wear and tear and will require some mechanical attention, it's a fantastic opportunity to own a vehicle at a fraction of the cost. Perfect for a mechanic's special or anyone looking for a solid base to restore!",
