    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, providing a comfortable and dependable driving experience. While the exterior and interior show some light signs of regular use, there are no major mechanical issues or significant damage. It is a solid, honest car that is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
