    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver despite some noticeable cosmetic and mechanical wear. The exterior has several scuffs, minor dents, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery shows signs of age with some staining and a small tear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car runs well, though it may soon require routine maintenance for wear-and-tear items like brake pads and tires. It is a solid choice for someone looking for functional transportation at an affordable price point.",
